  .col-xs-12.learnmore
    %h2.center 4 Students + 1 Senior Programmer x 3 months = 1 Minimum Viable Product

.row-fluid.descriptions
  .col-xs-12.col-lg-4.col-sm-4.col-md-4.students-description
    %h4
      %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-user
      Students

    %p If you are in your final year and love to code, drop us a note and want to join in this awesome program just drop us a note and we shall see what we can do. Space is seriously limited so do what you gotta do - we will select the most awesome of the awesome.

    %a.btn.btn-primary{href: 'https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1pXvc8U4UJXiE4PCAJhqLiJdK9rX3WTR-Sm0a54tLtSY/viewform'} I Want In!

  .col-xs-12.col-lg-4.col-sm-4.col-md-4.universities-description
    %h4
      %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-tower
      Universities

    %p If you are a lecturer and think there are some pretty amazing students in your class that would be that more amazing if they had a chance to join our completely free training program, you should forward this flyer to them and ask them to apply. 

    %a.btn.btn-primary{href: '#universities'} How Do I Get Involved?

  .col-xs-12.col-lg-4.col-sm-4.col-md-4.startups-description
    %h4
      %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-send
      Startups

    %p Everyone's got ideas, and if you can prove to us the market wants them drop us a line and we will take it under consideration. We are looking for early stage ideas.

    %p Remember - don't pitch an idea to us, pitch a product that people want.

    %a.btn.btn-primary{href: '#startups'} I Want an MVP

